stateDiagram-v2

    Idle --> Monitoring : SensorEvent#colon;#colon;Start
    Monitoring --> Error : SensorEvent#colon;#colon;DataReady(value)<br/>[ if *value>1000 ]
    Monitoring --> Idle : SensorEvent#colon;#colon;Stop
    Monitoring --> Error : SensorEvent#colon;#colon;Error
    Error --> Monitoring : SensorEvent#colon;#colon;Start
    Error --> Idle : SensorEvent#colon;#colon;Stop
